{
  "stem": "4693.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First, we are going in the rain and we are freezing to this degree.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the train had this big nails-- so if you lie next to the nail, your clothes was freezing to the nail, you know?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We arrived, we didn't know where, somewhere in the north.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We are unloaded-- it was already evening-- from the tracks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And put-- walked-- brought by tracks, and brought into a camp, concentration camp, and all assembled [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in an area of the camp.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were about thousands in the transport.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were already mixed with the Russians.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was October-- end of September or beginning of October, 1940.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was more or less one-- one year, October, I think, one year in the concentration camp almost-- in the jails.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Then this was a medical commission.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I noticed colossal disorder, how they were getting people through.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they determine that I am good for work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The next days, they called us to work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When they came to me, I came to-- I told them a lie, said the commission found me unable-- unsuitable for work.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It took them a month to find out that I was a liar.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "During this period, I was left inside the camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The camp, the concentration camps in Russia, inside the camp, were run by the inmates-- but only by the inmates whom the Russian authorities trusted.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they were the criminals.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were political people, some of those people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I made friends with them during the month, when I was inside the camp-- because it was empty.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because nobody was-- them, they are the administration end.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Nobody [INAUDIBLE] during the day.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
